<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.3.10">
<l>tēṉamar pūmpoḻil tillaic cittira kūṭama marnta</l>
<l>vāṉavar taṅkaḷpi rāṉai maṅkaiyar kōṉmaru vārtamūṉamar vēlkali kaṉṟi yoṇṭami ḻoṉpatō ṭoṉṟum tāṉivai kaṟṟaval lārmēl cārā tīviṉai tāṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>On those who are able to learn these nine-and-one splendid Tamil [verses]</l>
<l>By Kalikaṉṟi, king of those of Maṅkai,</l>
<l rend="indent">with a spear where remains the flesh of his foes,</l>
<l>About the celestials’ lord who remains in Citrakūṭam in Tillai</l>
<l>With gardens of blossoms where nectar remains, cruel fate will not adhere.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
